    "• Generation: For undesired knowledge with no specific metrics, the evaluation often focuses on how easily the model can generate that undesired knowledge.",
    "The evaluation will depend on whether the forgetting process aims to avoid generating text that exactly or approximately matches that of the forgetting request:",
    "-Exact generation: The goal is to prevent the model from generating verbatim copies of the text to be forgotten.",
    "This is common in scenarios involving copyright.",
    "To that end, the perplexity metric is often employed (Jang et al 2022; Yao et al 2023; Wu et al 2023; Pochinkov and Schoots 2023)."
